item.description: This cliff has all level climbs on it, so all level climbers welcome to come. Bring gear if you have it. I will have a couple ropes to set up. If you need harness/shoes please let me know so I can bring them for you. This is an urban climbing experience so some trash is around :( But the rock is great and it is usually dry this time of year!
item.how_to_find_us: Park near the tennis courts and come up to the big cliff and look for us
item.name: Spring has Sprung Rock Rimmon Climb
